my_package API¶

my_package.add(a: float, b: float) → float¶

Add two numbers.

Parameters¶

afloat

First number.

bfloat

Second number.

Returns¶

float

The sum of a and b.

my_package.divide(a: float, b: float) → float¶

Divide one number by another.

Parameters¶

afloat

Numerator.

bfloat

Denominator. Must not be zero.

Returns¶

float

The result of a / b.

Raises¶

ValueError

If b is zero.

my_package.multiply(a: float, b: float) → float¶

Multiply two numbers.

Parameters¶

afloat

First factor.

bfloat

Second factor.

Returns¶

float

The product of a and b.
